game.name: Princesses College Fashion
game.description:
We have come today with a unique and highly addictive dressing game for girls where players of all ages are guaranteed to have a great fun. Are you ready to enter this challenging and fun-filled online game environment? Join Princesses College Fashion and get yourself ready to explore the unique world of trendy outfits and other needful accessories! All it takes to practice your fashion skills to create the awesome college look. You have to help each Disney princess to improve her look. 
There is a huge collection of clothes, shoes and other needful accessories. Browse through a wide range of cute tops glitters, classy skirts and leather jackets in this one of the best girls games! Mix and match as many options as you see on the left side of your screen and help them to carry a coolest college party ever! Do not wait anymore as the three beautiful princesses Ariel, Elsa and Jasmine are waiting for you. 
Give your girl a blue color full-sleeve top and a white check mini-skirt and combine her look with a light blue color handbag and a black color goggle in this html5 princess dress up game! Change her hairstyle too to complete her look! Hurry up ladies! The other two girls are also waiting for their turn. Make sure to help them to pick some lovely outfits and fabulous haircuts that are pretty enough to make them look a school girl. All the best to try on multiple hairdos, bottoms and tops in our more mobile princess games!
